Vulkan Structure

Vulkan Class -> Instance Holder
|- 	Init Window - Instance 
|-  Create Instance - Instance 
|-  Setup Debug - Debug/Instance
|-  Create Surface - Instance 
|-  Choose Physical Device - 
|-  Create Logical Device - 
|-  Create Swap Chain - Renderer
|----  Create Swap Chain Image Views 
|-  Create Render Target - Renderer
|----  Create Render Target Image Views
|-  Create Render Pass - Renderer
|-  Create Descriptor Set Layout - Control
|-  Create Graphics Pipeline - Renderer
|-  Create Framebuffers - Renderer
|-  Create Command Pools - Control
|-  Create Vertex Buffer - Control
|-  Create Index Buffer - Control
|-  Create Uniform Buffer - Control
|-  Create Descriptor Pool - Control
|-  Create Descriptor Sets - Control 
|-  Create Render Command Buffer - Control
\-  Create Sync Objects - Control
